text: Serangoon North MRT station (CR9) is a future underground Mass Rapid Transit station on the Cross Island MRT line located on the boundary of Serangoon and Hougang planning areas, Singapore. ==History== The station was first announced on 25 January 2019 as part of the Cross Island Line (CRL). Construction will start in 2020 and expected to be completed by 2029. ==References== Category:Mass Rapid Transit (Singapore) stations
title: Serangoon North MRT station
